#Israel Aims to Vaccinate 2.25 Million Against #COVID19 in a Month

Israel hopes to vaccinate about 1/3 of its population in the coming month, possibly the 1st country to achieve this landmark.

About 280,000 Israelis received the #vaccine in Operation Lend a Shoulder's 1st week. https://t.co/EkjslR4hIG
